<div class="tip_number">TIP 56</div>
<div class="tip_contents">
            Male breast enlargement commonly occurs in adolescents, obese persons, or alcohol drinkers. It can be caused by a hormonal imbalance or certain medications, but on rare occasions may be a sign of cancer in the testicles or lungs or another serious ailment. It may or may not be associated with pain.
        </div>

